{"tid":2151814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【二戰歷史】【邱吉爾：We shall never surrender】面對納粹極權，我們絕不投降","createTime":"2020-08-11T14:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T16:07:28.000Z","uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c719b0a872148dc5b5e8fc8fd997671180522735","tid":2151814,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxCjXQ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxCjXQ7.png&h=46978e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aB0UMKE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaB0UMKE.png&h=af1e6c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">We shall never surrender<br />\n我們絕不投降</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗱，我只係講二戰歷史邱吉爾咋<br />\n絕無其他含義同影射<br />\n敬請各單位幹部及社會各持分者 (stakeholder) 垂注<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217c6171695bdd020cffb76de91d95e520c898a0","tid":2151814,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以陪伴到112個人？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2151813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2151813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"649245099f27c0f32258815c0e01ad08c1aa8b47","tid":2151814,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"Fear is a reaction<br />\nCourage is a decision"},{"pid":"5142b08855cf105b8e4900298a1ccf9467f10c41","tid":2151814,"uid":318300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"邱吉爾講得好, We shall never surrender <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac6a3eeeeb71d482b018668c9be953564eaa1bd","tid":2151814,"uid":74412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377587c638eaf1186b79bd210f1a9d3f3f5d7c4a","tid":2151814,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80c9aae2172700773b7b0cec51c329d251ed75f3","tid":2151814,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5142b08855cf105b8e4900298a1ccf9467f10c41","tid":2151814,"uid":318300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"邱吉爾講得好, We shall never surrender <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />We shall never surrender x 2"},{"pid":"b5e28987f6bebeaf6a9c7444dcf19d70fca3bb6b","tid":2151814,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"當時二戰，納粹興兵，四出侵略，攻城掠地，<br />\n尤其對猶太人，納粹每日都拉人殺人。<br />\n歐洲各國，山河破落，生靈塗炭，血流成河。<br />\n<br />\n黑雲壓城城欲摧。<br />\n<br />\n英倫三島，岌岌可危之際，<br />\n面對納粹極權，竟然有人有勇氣企出嚟，<br />\n振臂一呼，大大聲講一句：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">&ldquo;We shall never surrender&ldquo;</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這句說話，這一句口號，真係好振奮人心。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗱，我講二戰英國邱吉爾咋<br />\n絕無含沙射影<br />\n千祈咪誤會呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c530d178a72a496684f675d56fc6b5c1d0fc18d","tid":2151814,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:17:55.000Z","msg":"英國人話香港人梗似英國人"},{"pid":"3480042314cd9c9e383709e6b37c047d11d8eeea","tid":2151814,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"We shall go on to the end<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4005e46feb80ece3316f0e4d8e3400dc1a181ec","tid":2151814,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:04:11.000Z","msg":"佢哋當時就淨係shall fight on land , sea and air. 宜家就係fight on 所有戰線，支支其實係唔用真槍實彈咁同全世界打仗，低調侵略。"},{"pid":"b6eeb34ea0c134ec3652aef53dd3eed88d5b10cd","tid":2151814,"uid":26001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"發覺成個香港好似越戰越強咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}